You or agents will get a basic hourly salary however, everyone's permanency on this job depends on results. Agents should create 10+ leads per day and 3+ of their leads need to be verified by our verification team. 

You o yourr team needs:

-Cold calling experience
-Hard working attitude
-Good English skills
-Basic computer skills
-Capability to work 8:00 AM to 4:00 PM Pacific time (U.S.A)

Your team will find our leads by calling H^sites^H like: Yelp, Manta, Superpages, Google, Maps, Yellow Pages, Bing Places. Once they read the short script to the decision maker they just need to move on to the next call. (It's a simple task)

If this job description sounds like your team, you are more than welcome to apply and hopefully we can do this job together!

title: Python H^Web^H H^Scraping^H Script for Mobile Phone Numbers
description:
This is what I need done for 240,000 valid mobile phone numbers a month. Step by step process below using python scripts:

1. Get the data from the source. I already have someone to do this part and I provide you with the CSV full of data.

2. Find the correct addresses using https://vericora.com/ I provde you with the owners name, city, and state to do this. I need you to find the correct street addresses that match the city, state, and name. You can create a python script to do this.

3. Then go to truepeoplesearch.com to find the wireless phone numbers. You have the owners names and correct addresses to do this. You can create a python script to do this.

4. Verify those wireless phone numbers are correct with peoplesearchnow.com If the names of the people match up with the phone number then keep the record otherwise delete it. I need you to use this H^website^H to verify that the mobile phone numbers you found using the previous H^website^H are their mobile phone numbers so if their name comes up on this H^website^H matching the owners name when you search their phone number then it is correct. You can create a python script to do this.
